snippet.textDisplay:
Pomme paillasson

How to read french word.
When vowels AEIOU are beside consonants the consonants are silent. SSON
When two vowels are together the 2nd vowel are read. PAI
When cosonants are together the second consonant are sound. LLA
Vowel at the end of the word are silent. MME
